                <p>Taking the first step toward better mental health is a brave and important decision. We are here to make the process as clear and comfortable as possible. This page provides information about what to expect when you become a patient at Altos Psychiatry.</p>
                
                <h3>What to Expect on Your First Visit</h3>
                <p>Your initial appointment is a comprehensive 60-90 minute evaluation. This is a conversation, not an interrogation. We will discuss your current challenges, personal and family history, and your goals for treatment. It is a collaborative session designed to create a personalized plan that feels right for you.</p>

